ynergism', 'The risk of hepatic injury should be considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/4458/', '[1] "Product Information. Adcetris (brentuximab vedotin)." Seattle Genetics Inc, Bothell, WA.', 'Salicylic acid, Choline salicylate, Ziconotide, Diflunisal, Methoxyflurane, Salsalate, Acetylsalicylic acid, Oxymorphone, Oxycodone, Methadone, Pentazocine, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
