d fruit and probable active ingredients." Clin Pharmacol Ther 68 (2000): 468-77', 'Salicylic acid, Salsalate, Choline salicylate, Diflunisal, Methoxyflurane, Naloxone', 'Brivaracetam, Rufinamide, Methsuximide, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Paramethadione, Perampanel, Fenfluramine, Eslicarbazepine, Ganaxolone, Phensuximide, More', 1767369485);
